<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=2193&amp;p=11026#p11026"><![CDATA[
There will be some item below Programs on the Customize Start Menu tab which does not have a Label. When the Label field is empty, it shows &lt;No Text&gt;. For example, you may have the &quot;Recent programs&quot; item added which might say &lt;No text&gt; because it has text no label by default.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Mon Feb 17, 2014 8:59 pm</p><hr />
